section.container.content-section.text-center(id="demo")
    .demo-section
        .container(style="min-height:590px;")
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
                h2 Demos
                .col-md-6
                    a(href="./demo1")
                        img(src="img/demo1.png" alt="Weapons 3D menu")
                        p(style="font-size:1em;") An example of a 3D menu similar to the original Tomb Raider 2 menu, it contains some weapons and a similar background. The menu control is binded to two html buttons and also the name of the selected element is displayed in a html tag under the menu.
                .col-md-6
                    a(href="./demo2")
                        img(src="img/demo2.png" alt="Black and white websites menu")
                        p(style="font-size:1em;") An example of a 3D menu featuring the logos of some interesting projects. The menu control is binded to the keyboard, also the enter key is binded to the action of every item on the menu, which is going to the project's website.
                .col-md-6
                    a(href="/demo3")
                        img(src="img/demo3.png" alt="Golden SVG icons menu")
                        p(style="font-size:1em;") This example features a 3D menu created out of SVG shapes to 3D icons using Blender. It also demonstrates events risen from an object action, that can be captured and custom javascript functions can be called when activating a menu option.
